twifrf.pl
===================

command line tool for sync friendfeed group with twitter account

INSTALLATION

    #init db
    twifrf.pl -init -twi -frf -f storage.xml

    # do sync
    twifrf.pl -twi -frf -f storage.xml

     #publish new messages only from friendfeed
     twifrf.pl -frf -f storage.xml

DEPENDENCIES

For use is necessary following software:

    * Flow
    * XML::Flow
    * Net::Twitter

Project site: https://github.com/zag/lveeboteg

